flowchart TB
AG["AI AGENT<br/>Claude · Cursor · Codex · Devin · Copilot"]
AG ==> ACT["agent action<br/>file write or shell command"]
ACT ==> P["LAYER 1 · PRETOOL HOOK<br/>intercepts before execution"]
P ==> ENG["scan_content engine<br/>content + command analysis (6 layers)"]
ENG ==> SEV{"hostile?"}
SEV ==>|"no"| OK["PERMITE<br/>action proceeds normally"]
SEV ==>|"yes"| BLK["BLOQUEIA<br/>exit 2 · nothing executes"]
BLK -. "reached disk?" .-> DM["LAYER 2 · DAEMON<br/>watches the filesystem in background"]
DM ==> Q["QUARENTENA<br/>isolates the file · no delete"]
Q ==> HUM["human decides<br/>restore · purge"]
ACT -. "Linux · parallel" .-> K["LAYER 3 · eBPF (kernel)<br/>containment net in case the pretool<br/>is disabled or bypassed"]
K ==> EP["BLOCKS in the kernel<br/>-EPERM"]
OK -.-> LOG["100% local log<br/>nothing leaves your machine"]
BLK -.-> LOG
EP -.-> LOG

